    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Author：lambda</p><hr><h3 id="参考："><a href="#参考：" class="headerlink" title="参考："></a>参考：</h3><ul><li>Hexo: <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/</a></li><li>主题：<a href="https://www.haomwei.com/technology/maupassant-hexo.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">maupassant</a></li><li>安装：<a href="https://www.cnblogs.com/fengxiongZz/p/7707219.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.cnblogs.com/fengxiongZz/p/7707219.html</a></li></ul><p>下面大体说一下安装步骤，详细过程可参考其他博客  </p><h5 id="1-下载并安装-Nodejs"><a href="#1-下载并安装-Nodejs" class="headerlink" title="1.下载并安装 Nodejs"></a>1.下载并安装 <a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nodejs</a></h5><figure class="highlight crmsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 测试安装是否成功</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">node</span> <span class="title">-v</span></span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="2-下载并安装-Git"><a href="#2-下载并安装-Git" class="headerlink" title="2.下载并安装 Git"></a>2.下载并安装 <a href="https://git-scm.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Git</a></h5><h5 id="3-在github中创建名为LambdaRan-github-io的仓库"><a href="#3-在github中创建名为LambdaRan-github-io的仓库" class="headerlink" title="3.在github中创建名为LambdaRan.github.io的仓库"></a>3.在github中创建名为LambdaRan.github.io的仓库</h5><h5 id="4-选择一个目录存放博客，如E-Blog"><a href="#4-选择一个目录存放博客，如E-Blog" class="headerlink" title="4.选择一个目录存放博客，如E:/Blog"></a>4.选择一个目录存放博客，如E:/Blog</h5><h5 id="5-安装Hexo"><a href="#5-安装Hexo" class="headerlink" title="5.安装Hexo"></a>5.安装Hexo</h5><figure class="highlight cmake"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm <span class="keyword">install</span> -g hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line">hexo -v <span class="comment">#测试是否安装成功</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo init <span class="comment">#初始化目录</span></span><br><span class="line">npm <span class="keyword">install</span> <span class="comment">#安装所需要的组件</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo g <span class="comment">#首次体验Hexo</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo s <span class="comment">#开启服务器</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="6-将Hexo与Github-page联系起来"><a href="#6-将Hexo与Github-page联系起来" class="headerlink" title="6.将Hexo与Github page联系起来"></a>6.将Hexo与Github page联系起来</h5><ol><li>生成ssh密钥对</li><li>修改主_config.yml文件，如下<figure class="highlight less"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">deploy</span>:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">repo</span>: git<span class="variable">@github</span>.<span class="attribute">com</span>:LambdaRan/LambdaRan.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">branch</span>: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h5 id="7-编译提交-hexo-g-hexo-d"><a href="#7-编译提交-hexo-g-hexo-d" class="headerlink" title="7. 编译提交 hexo g hexo d"></a>7. 编译提交 hexo g hexo d</h5><h5 id="8-淘宝NPM镜像"><a href="#8-淘宝NPM镜像" class="headerlink" title="8. 淘宝NPM镜像"></a>8. <a href="https://npm.taobao.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">淘宝NPM镜像</a></h5><h5 id="9-安装maupassant主题"><a href="#9-安装maupassant主题" class="headerlink" title="9. 安装maupassant主题"></a>9. 安装<a href="https://www.haomwei.com/technology/maupassant-hexo.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">maupassant主题</a></h5><h5 id="10-其他"><a href="#10-其他" class="headerlink" title="10. 其他"></a>10. 其他</h5><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/ganzhilin520/article/details/79047249" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/ganzhilin520/article/details/79047249</a><br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/35e197cb1273" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.jianshu.com/p/35e197cb1273</a></p>]]></content>
    
